+/**
+ * eCryptfs: Linux filesystem encryption layer
+ *
+ * Copyright (c) 1997-2003 Erez Zadok
+ * Copyright (c) 2001-2003 Stony Brook University
+ * Copyright (c) 2005 International Business Machines Corp.
